		<title type="html"><![CDATA[BuddyPress &#8211; Bringer of Open Social Network Bliss?]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.nixonmcinnes.co.uk/2008/04/01/buddypress-bringer-of-open-social-network-bliss/" />
		<id>http://www.nixonmcinnes.co.uk/2008/04/01/buddypress-bringer-of-open-social-network-bliss/</id>
		<updated>2008-04-02T15:50:36Z</updated>
